{"tid":1643034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，搵人選翠怡區議員(青衣人入)","createTime":"2019-10-10T03:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T07:22:12.000Z","uid":146944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa6af10ca3b2057cdf747c1574cdbf05ab87ba1","tid":1643034,"uid":146944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"話說，翠怡選區呢10幾年都係由自稱獨立ge<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">張慧晶</span></strong>做區議員。<br />\n講真，住左咁耐，除左每次提名前後/投票前後有見過呢個女人，其他時間真係影都未見過。<br />\n條友個底，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">又前自由黨又前新民黨</span></ins></strong>，但又o係到話自己支持反送中。<br />\n但係而家仲未有人出黎同佢爭，唔係由自動當選呀嘛？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74w41uy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74w41uy.jpg&h=1a1e68d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n真係見到佢個樣就燥"},{"pid":"1ce54e96049a0a860a210f0f5cc8e01e4dd72582","tid":1643034,"uid":59854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"反咩送中 明明麥美娟手下"},{"pid":"42b3a48c4a35259373a7d3a35af16fffe78f908d","tid":1643034,"uid":146944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"仲未有人同佢一齊爭 真係好撚驚"},{"pid":"871ff9dc94eafc792add7f8263ba327556f37058","tid":1643034,"uid":204180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QNozSK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QNozSK.jpg&h=6aeac0bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ea13aa0845670f8651eae09daea130a22e3d193","tid":1643034,"uid":204180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"871ff9dc94eafc792add7f8263ba327556f37058","tid":1643034,"uid":204180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QNozSK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QNozSK.jpg&h=6aeac0bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱